@Deprecated public abstract class AbstractDoubleBidirectionalIterator extends AbstractDoubleIterator implements DoubleBidirectionalIterator
Deprecated.
As of fastutil 8 this class is no longer necessary, as its previous abstract methods are now default methods of the type-specific interface.
An abstract class facilitating the creation of type-specific bidirectional iterators.
